            <div class="col-12">
                <p>Hi. I'm Joe Daigle, owner of Clean Gutter Co.</p>

                <p>Did you know that every year, over 500,000 ladder-related injuries are treated in emergency rooms across the United States? That's a lot of falls!</p>

                <p>Why take the risk, just to clean a gutter? But how else will you get 'em cleaned?</p>

                <p>And if you hire someone, they'll just climb up ladders themselves, and could fall just as easily. Right?</p>

