                <p>And because we don't have to move a ladder every time we clean an arms-length of gutter, we can get to work a lot quicker! Without having to hurry our work, or bang ladders all over your house. Doesn't that sound more like it?</p>

                <p>As a veteran-owned business, you can rest assured that we're putting our best foot forward, each and every day. You can count on us to provide top-notch service, and to treat you with the utmost respect and courtesy. It's my promise to you.</p>

                <p>If at any time, you are not satisfied with our service, please <a class="text-link" href="mailto:joe@cleangutterco.com">email me directly</a>, and I will personally address your concerns.</p>

                <p>So, what are you waiting for? <a class="text-link" href="tel:1-478-261-1140">Give us a call</a>, and get the safe, professional cleaning your gutters deserve!</p>

